data.meta_description: Futsal-2018 - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Futsal is a variant of football played on a smaller court and is gaining popularity in the Philippines. It is well-suited to be played almost anywhere as it only requires a basketball or tennis-sized court. Futsal emphasizes technical skills, quick decision-making, and precision which improves players' abilities in other sports as well. While interest is growing among students and professionals in Manila, there remains limited information available online for Filipinos wanting to learn more about and play futsal.
